Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:04.79,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD8F0E8&\4c&H616484&\pos(420,389)}第四话 谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 快去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在学校过的怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以前问她都说很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次喜形于色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜不自禁了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是恋爱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 我的爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 孩子他爸说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:19:25.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯:瑤瑤 老虎　校譯:キョン　時間:キョン　後期:風一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝过幸福的滋味后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛就把不知幸福滋味的时候忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独占
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定我现在已经把这辈子的幸福都用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 就是眼睛很细的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 中学时就是个问题学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老师弄哭 还和班里所有男生都打过架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是干过许多比这更厉害的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我的眼睛可没那么细
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 中学就已经是百人斩了太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能满足我的男人有100个么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话就带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你们鉴定下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光辉历史根本不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 因为是谣言嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的眼睛根本没那么细
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要比你想的细
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是假的 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子放的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你始作俑者是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子为了提高自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在利用风早同学和吉田同学还有矢野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑的我肚子痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那里的拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同学 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:03:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和全班的男生都打过架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超喜欢男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中学时代就已经是百人斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考试的要点笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我试着做了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能派上用处的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心怀感激的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 矢野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去影像店借怪谈的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话能不能给我推荐几部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笔记借我复印下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我替你打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮到别人真是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超纯白色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 风早同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小老头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞 我想快点去教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 喝着喝着酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碗的周围有几个人在不断的转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转啊转转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一个个就掉到碗里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫黑沼的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为和那个女孩对视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会不断发生奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐她旁边不是知道很多么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙诅咒之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信我自己看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所看到黑沼是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐观的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经和黑沼搞上了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说不出话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 别再往下说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后然后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小痞叫去听小老头的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然昨天说了独占这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞上了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看她了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 额头…残念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在感受幸福的每一天里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起开心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都认为周围没朋友是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这样的事根本没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我从未体会过的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填满了内心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像第一次收到的礼物那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同学 吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 好像最近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣言满天飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得变得越来越夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老爷爷打的头破血流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有扶起跌倒的老爷爷这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说矢野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些援交的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然我们是完全不相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说那个放出谣言的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会一下子谣言四起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有点过分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然放出那样的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到周围比以前更怕我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 诗乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近关于你的谣言变得很厉害唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵感 诅咒什么的谣言诗乃也已经听说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然误会很难消除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子说朋友坏话什么的根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也不像以前那么介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的人对我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得贞子给人的感觉变得柔和了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都说是贞子说的 贞子说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 有人恶意中伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是对贞子还是对我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子的谣言和平常不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫矢野和吉田对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着 听下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 跟我走趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉朋友是像吉田同学和矢野同学那样的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当看到她们2人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会觉得她们很喜欢对方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没那么不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我很喜欢她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能成为朋友的那一天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会觉得真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球部的极密练习表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我交给龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个家伙都让我觉得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句话到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没问过贞子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们直接问贞子是不是朋友的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会很微妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直笑着的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里坐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很认真的问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要如实的回答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我们很喜欢你 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜欢我们么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说喜欢 不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子 让你困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让她们明白了我的心意么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但矢野同学和吉田同学的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却看上去没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛连我也感到很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么方法能让她们打起精神来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然得寸进尺到把吉田和矢野当作靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且连风早都随意使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个厉害的人呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 什么~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始我从贞子转为幕后黑手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 矢野和吉田那灰暗的传言真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰暗的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些才情绪低落的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们伤心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是贞子的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 都是因为贞子在她们周围
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这么被贞子纠缠下去 绝对会人气下滑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同学和吉田同学只是温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是那样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为贞子在她们周围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在她们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她们受到了伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我的身边 风早同学不知哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会像矢野同学和吉田同学那样受到伤害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了吗 过于那个小老头的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见过的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看见过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是不在他们身边会好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我不能留在他们身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 眼睛红得好像彻夜痛哭过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你的眼睛不也是好像熬夜一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们的谣言是贞子放出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我也开始迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天听过贞子的回答以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 至少贞子的心里是不喜欢我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 你问的是关于“喜欢”的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她立刻回答“喜欢” 那谣言绝对不是她传出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定会相信的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子是不可能会散播谣言的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我百分百的相信着的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在却不知道如果是真的我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信谣言并不是贞子传出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌那么想的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛红红的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我让你们情绪低落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子她是在道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“让你们情绪低落了”是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是贞子把谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不这样想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了“对不起 不是喜欢”的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那一件都让人无法忍受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太自以为是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为自己对贞子来说是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 以为她是真的喜欢我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同学和吉田同学她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远比我想像的要伤的深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快点找到散播谣言的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替她们澄清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同学和吉田同学并不是什么靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是温柔的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把这些告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道解除误会的办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散播谣言的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(434,432)}听好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让她们快点恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复成笑着的矢野同学和吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的应该是她们俩才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像在躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么伤到你的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什么让你讨厌的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 风早同学什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算 就算风早同学真的做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也绝对不会讨厌你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么都绝对不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(423,431)}马上考试了 你还是很轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(423,431)}就算去折腾也不会怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早同学 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明答应过不论发生什么都绝不避开你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我留在你的身边会给你带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想避开你 但是远离你会好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想在你们身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开你们是对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飘飘浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未到达天空就破灭消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们想要的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管想要永远留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找寻到了属于我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:34.66,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,360)}第五话 决心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说很重要的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话 决心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里为你带来动画“好想告诉你”最新情报的告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位分别是为黑沼爽子配音的能登麻美子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和为风早翔太配音的浪川大辅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每周都在感动中配音 希望这份心意能够传给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周也是紧紧张张的 继续期待下周
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周将会有椿姬彩菜小姐的初次亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们下周见 告诉你

